					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td><a href="https://pentimenti.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="citrus-link">Pentimenti.ai</a></td>
						<td>Platform that specializes in developing AI solutions to simplify and streamline the sales and tender process.</td>
						<td>AI / Sales</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td><a href="https://rotobot.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="citrus-link">Rotobot.ai</a></td>
						<td>AI-driven fantasy football chatbot utilizing up-to-date sports data</td>
						<td>AI & Sports Analytics</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td><a href="https://intermate.de/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="citrus-link">Intermate.de</a></td>
